parameters: I'm not very thirsty right now.
There was a vending machine that had chocolate mint candy.
I'm not very thirsty right now.
I found Akane with a blank expression on their face.

They tilted their head, closed their eyes, and wandered
around while crossing their arms...
They seem to be troubled about something.
But what were you doing here?

Akane, while suddenly smiling, points at the vending machine
with her fingertips.
At the end point, there was ramune.
It's not just any ramune! Look at it again!

It's not just any ramune, no matter where you look, it's
ramune...

I wanted to try it once, but I couldn't find it in the
end. But I found it here.
No, I don't understand the meaning...

Why does something like chocolate mint ramune actually
exist?
...Hikaru, are you the type who dislikes chocolate mint...?

Akane, who had been overflowing with energy until now,
suddenly looks down as if it were a lie.

Ku... If I'm asked whether I like it or not, then of
course...

Ehehe, what's this, surprising me! So Hikaru also likes
chocolate mint after all!

After exchanging a silly conversation, she returned to her
usual energetic self.

If I'm asked whether I actually like it or not, I
don't really have a preference.

It's not sold out! There are definitely still some in
stock!

stare at me.
